section.section:
The notice must contain the following information:
a demand that the matter be referred to the Office of Administrative Hearings for a contested case hearing in accordance with § 10-205(c)(2) of the State Government Article;
the names, addresses, and telephone numbers of the Commission, the business entity's representatives, and any other parties;
a reference to this title; and
a summary of the Commission's findings and recommendations that are being submitted for resolution to the administrative law judge for the contested case hearing.
